CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 11, 1957, pg. A14 reads: "Lovely Models who showed fascinating fashions Sunday at the Anna B. Heldman Center, included some of the top style talent in town. The event was the annual fashion show given by the Pittsburgh Scholarship Guild, and the above pretty-pretty maids and matrons made beautiful scenery. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of seven women modeling light colored dresses, posed in front of dark curtain in Anna B. Heldman Center for Pittsburgh Scholarship Guild's annual fashion show
